Miharu to the left.

265
00:17:38,958 --> 00:17:41,125
Miharu to the front and back.
Hither and tither.

266
00:17:41,208 --> 00:17:43,208
Miharu as far as
the eye can see!

267
00:17:43,291 --> 00:17:44,458
[FUKUYAMA laughs]

268
00:17:44,541 --> 00:17:46,416
I'm in Miharu heaven!

269
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:49,166
It is up to me
to save the world.

270
00:17:49,250 --> 00:17:51,083
I accept the
awesome responsibility

271
00:17:51,166 --> 00:17:54,166
of acting as
humanity's savior.

272
00:17:54,250 --> 00:17:57,500
It's no use
trying to stop me.

273
00:17:57,583 --> 00:17:59,333
Miharu, hold me!

274
00:18:03,625 --> 00:18:06,583
I didn't know a person
could be that stupid.

275
00:18:15,416 --> 00:18:19,250
I know she's close.
I have a feeling.

276
00:18:27,000 --> 00:18:29,375
[FUKUYAMA panting]

277
00:18:29,458 --> 00:18:34,208
Young man!
Young man come here!

278
00:18:37,166 --> 00:18:38,250
You called?

279
00:18:38,333 --> 00:18:39,791
That's some fine work
you did out there,

280
00:18:39,875 --> 00:18:41,458
thinning that herd
of pink devils.

281
00:18:41,541 --> 00:18:42,625
We owe you one.

282
00:18:42,708 --> 00:18:45,500
No need for thanks.
It was my pleasure.

283
00:18:45,583 --> 00:18:47,208
You've got grit, boy.

284
00:18:47,291 --> 00:18:50,041
I have a big favor
to ask of you.

285
00:18:50,125 --> 00:18:53,916
Here you go.

286
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:54,916
It's a...

287
00:18:55,000 --> 00:18:56,583
You're looking at
the only weapon

288
00:18:56,666 --> 00:18:59,458
left in our arsenal.
Please take it.

289
00:18:59,541 --> 00:19:02,041
We think this just might
attract their attention,

290
00:19:02,125 --> 00:19:03,708
and it can withstand
a lot of abuse.

291
00:19:03,791 --> 00:19:05,375
We beg of you.

292
00:19:05,458 --> 00:19:09,541
They're destroying what it
took us 3 years to get going.

293
00:19:09,625 --> 00:19:14,583
All right then. I will
stop them. This I swear.

294
00:19:19,875 --> 00:19:22,250
Kazuharu Fukuyama. Go!

295
00:19:23,833 --> 00:19:29,583
Attention Miharus. Who's in
the mood for a big banana?

296
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:35,250
Ba-na-na, ba-na-na, ba-na-na...

297
00:19:35,333 --> 00:19:37,166
Peel this!

298
00:19:38,083 --> 00:19:40,541
ba-na-na, ba-na-na, ba-na-na...

299
00:20:13,125 --> 00:20:15,833
Trust yourself. It's her.

300
00:20:26,333 --> 00:20:27,916
Yukinari?

301
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:30,375
Miharu, I'm so glad.

302
00:20:30,458 --> 00:20:32,041
Where am I?

303
00:20:32,125 --> 00:20:35,333
It's kind of a long story.

304
00:20:36,250 --> 00:20:37,625
Miharu?

305
00:20:37,708 --> 00:20:39,875
I think... I had a nightmare.

306
00:20:39,958 --> 00:20:41,416
Nightmare?

307
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:44,666
Yeah. A very scary one.

308
00:20:44,750 --> 00:20:46,583
Oh, I drank some
delicious water,

309
00:20:46,666 --> 00:20:50,041
and I got dizzy,
and my body felt really hot.

310
00:20:50,125 --> 00:20:52,500
And the world started
spinning in circles,

311
00:20:52,583 --> 00:20:53,750
and then... and then...

312
00:20:53,833 --> 00:20:54,791
Miharu...

313
00:20:54,875 --> 00:20:55,916
Huh?

314
00:20:56,000 --> 00:21:00,958
You're fine. I'm here with you.

315
00:21:02,791 --> 00:21:04,583
Yukinari...

316
00:21:27,208 --> 00:21:28,875
What is that?

317
00:21:28,958 --> 00:21:31,458
Aww, this one's closed, too.

318
00:21:31,541 --> 00:21:33,916
A lot of the food stores
have been closed lately.

319
00:21:34,000 --> 00:21:36,166
I don't remember that sign.

320
00:21:36,250 --> 00:21:39,250
There's something
written on it. Let's see...

321
00:21:39,333 --> 00:21:42,375
"In honor of humanity's savior."

322
00:21:43,083 --> 00:21:45,541
Hey, Yukinari,
what does that mean?

323
00:21:45,625 --> 00:21:49,291
No idea. It's a
bit of a walk,

324
00:21:49,375 --> 00:21:53,125
but how about we try the
market the next town over.

325
00:21:53,208 --> 00:21:54,583
Sounds tasty.

